short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows notifications about various events in TeamCity

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TeamCity is a CI/CD server software developed by JetBrains. This extension enables browser notifications about various events like build failures and assigned investigations.
